channel.title: Posts on Code by Nate Finch

item.title: Something New
item.description: This is the first post of my new blog. You may see old posts showing up behind here, those have been pulled in from my personal blog at blog.natefinch.com. I’ve decided to split off my programming posts so that people who only want to see the coding stuff don’t have to see my personal posts, and people that only want to see my personal stuff don’t have to get inundated with programming posts.
